1) Rename the selected file perl.xml

2) Place the perl.xml file at:
   Either copy the downloaded XML file to ~/.kde/share/apps/katepart/syntax/ or to the global $(PREFIX)/share/apps/katepart/syntax/ directory

For the latest version go to
http://kate-editor.org/downloads/syntax_highlighting

Or see the repository:
http://websvn.kde.org/trunk/KDE/kdelibs/kate/syntax/data/
